Below is a single self-contained HTML file that implements real-time email validation using a regular expression. It changes the input border to green when the text matches the regex and red when it does not. The page also includes a visible explanation about why regex can't fully validate RFC-compliant email addresses and suggests better practical alternatives for production use.

