<section style="margin-top:18px;">
  <h3>Explanation (short)</h3>
  <p>
    Vulnerable mode shows how concatenating untrusted input into a query-like expression can allow the input to change the expression's logic (for example adding OR 1=1 makes the WHERE always true).
