  <div class="card" role="region" aria-label="Email validation demo">
    <h1>Email validation demo (regex-based, real-time)</h1>
    <p class="lead">Type an email address below. The input border turns green if the value matches the regex, red if it does not. This demo also explains why regex checks are limited and what to use in production.</p>

    <form id="form" novalidate>
      <div class="field">
        <label for="email">Email</label>
        <input id="email" type="text" autocomplete="email" inputmode="email" placeholder="you@example.com" aria-describedby="explain" />
        <div id="live-note" class="note small">Start typing to see live feedback.</div>
        <div class="hint">Toggle the regex below to see stricter/looser matches.</div>
      </div>

      <div class="controls" style="flex:0 0 220px; flex-direction:column; align-items:flex-end;">
        <button type="button" id="check" class="primary">Check now</button>
        <button type="button" id="clear">Clear</button>
        <label style="display:flex; gap:8px; align-items:center; margin-top:10px; font-size:13px;">
