<body>
  <h1>Memory Leak Demo: Event listeners & retained DOM refs (not GC bug)</h1>
  <div class="small">
    Two side-by-side demos. Left: "Leaking version" — widgets are removed visually but internal references & event listeners are not cleaned, causing retained objects. Right: "Fixed version" — listeners and references are removed properly.
