  <h1>Shopping Cart: floating-point pitfalls vs fixed cents</h1>
  <p>This demo shows why using JavaScript Number with naive === comparisons and arithmetic can produce surprising results for decimal prices (e.g., 4.99). The right approach here is to handle money in integer cents (or use a decimal library).</p>

